textBox.richText: The Idiap Biometric group at ICB

Most of the team attended last week the International Conference on Biometrics in Madrid. From right to left (up): Nesli Erdogmus, Ivana Cingovska, André Anjos, Sébastien Marcel, Manuel Günther, Elie El Khoury and Flavio Tarsetti (Engineering team). From right to left (down): Jukka Maatta Komulainen (visiting researcher at Idiap in 2012) and Tiago de Freitas Pereira (visiting student in 2012). Sadly, Laurent El Shafey was not able to join us.
Most of the Biometric group from Idiap at ICB 2013
